title: Return of the Blossoming
description:
Chung Myung, The 13th Disciple of the Great Flowery Mountain Sect, One of the 3 Great Swordsmen, the Plum Blossom Sword Saint, defeated Chun Ma, who has brought destruction and disarray onto the world.
After the battle, he breathes his last breath on top of the headquarter mountain of the Devil’s Worship Sect. But he is reborn after 100 years in the body of a child.
What? The Flowery Mountain Sect has fallen? What kind of nonsense is that!?
